survey_response.review_text: I was in a lot of pain because of a decayed tooth for over a week. I, however, resisted visiting a dentist because of my inherent fear of needles. When it got unbearable, I booked an appointment with Dr Sulabhi on my daughter's recommendation and I must say, she was right. Dr Sulabhi is extremely professional in her approach, is a very patient listener and took efforts to explain to me the procedure. She carried out the procedure with precision and meticulously and ensured it was pain free for me. I would highly recommend her to everyone else seeking a pain free and comfortable dental experience.

Absolutely wonderful! ** ******* *** *** **** *** *** **** ***** They are extremely professional, kind, and talented. To be honest, I've never had a better, easy going painless experience with a dentist. I'm so impressed and satisfied that every chance I get I recommend Bombay Dental Centre to anyone that wants the best dentist in Mumbai. As a side note...the technology she uses is over the top...super high tech state of the art equipment makes it seem so simple. With Dr's steady hand, expertise and supportive team, *** ***** *** *** *******

All in all, I am happy and would easily recommend getting tooth treatments done here.

I am completely satisfied with the outcome and will highly recommend her.
